OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1774246422
OL,3,CAround #1.8bn in business rates
OL,4,Cpredicted to be handed back to firms
OL,6,FMany firms are expecting to face
OL,7,Fhigher bills due to updates to
OL,8,Frateable values ` the property
OL,9,Fvaluations that the tax payments are
OL,10,Fbased on ` which come into force next
OL,11,Fmonth and are based on calculations
OL,12,Ffrom 2024.
OL,14,FA number of sectors, such as hotels,
OL,15,Fhave said firms are expecting higher
OL,16,Fbills as a result despite a reduction
OL,17,Fin the multiplier used to calculate
OL,18,Fthe property tax bills.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/5
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
