FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1774246422
OL,3,CAround #1.8bn in business rates
OL,4,Cpredicted to be handed back to firms
OL,6,FThe fresh data for setting the latest
OL,7,Fmultipliers showed that ministers have
OL,8,Fforecasted a #3.59 billion reduction
OL,9,Fin rateable value due to potential
OL,10,Fsuccessful appeals for the 2026 local
OL,11,Fratings lists. This is expected to
OL,12,Fresult in a roughly #1.8 billion
OL,13,Freturn from appeals.
OL,15,FBusinesses can launch a check,
OL,16,Fchallenge and appeal (CCA) process
OL,17,Fwhere they disagree with business
OL,18,Frates calculations.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/5
