OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1774246422
OL,3,CAround #1.8bn in business rates
OL,4,Cpredicted to be handed back to firms
OL,6,FNevertheless, corrections following
OL,7,Fappeals can take a significant time to
OL,8,Fcrystalise.
OL,10,FRyan said the data reveals that 8% of
OL,11,Fthe projected corrections are forecast
OL,12,Fto take place in the 2026/27 financial
OL,13,Fyear, with 13% of this a year later.
OL,15,FAlex Probyn, principal and practice
OL,16,Fleader at Ryan, said: "If a large
OL,17,Fproportion of adjustment is forecast
OL,18,Fto fall into the next rating cycle,
OL,19,Fthen that has implications for
OL,20,Fcertainty and planning.
OL,26,@xD@WOU
