OL,3,CAround #1.8bn in business rates
OL,4,Cpredicted to be handed back to firms
OL,6,F"Business rates liabilities feed
OL,7,Fdirectly into investment and capital
OL,8,Fexpenditure decisions. Timely
OL,9,Fresolution matters."
OL,11,FThe Government is currently consulting
OL,12,Fon the future direction of business
OL,13,Frates through an ongoing Call for
OL,14,FEvidence
